description: Represent an end user's data gathered from a form template. All FormData belongs to a single FormGroup.

formDataId.description: The system issued identifier that uniquely identifies this object.

groupId.description: The identifier of the group that manages this data. Required

name.description: User provided name for this submission. Required

createdBy.description: Id of the user that created this object

createdOn.description: The date this object was originally created.

modifiedOn.description: The date this object was last modified created.

dataFileHandleId.description: The identifier of the data file for this object.
